AniGame BOT 19-Jul-20 04:22 AM
Command: raid [Other shortcut names: rd]
The group command for Raid Battling.
raid battle [battle_amount=1]
Battles you in your dungeon location. NOT COMPLETE
raid energy
Shows your Raid Energy when you're in a raid.
raid forfeit
...
raid join <raid_code>
Joins and accepts the raid challenge!
raid kick <user>
Kicks out a user from your lobby. You can only do so if you are the Raid Lobby Leader.
raid leave
Leaves a raid lobby if you are in one and it hasn't started.
raid party
Checks out your raid lobby/party!
raid redeem
...

For when raids fail to work.
